{"title":"设计师能用OpenClaw做什么？","slug":"naidlfq53mc9ahn7","summary":"作为 UX/UI 设计师，我们的核心工作是 定义问题、梳理用户旅程（User Journey）、设计交互状态（States）以及确保最终的视觉与研发交付 。 Figma 等工具已经把“静态界面”和“基础原型”做到了极致，但 UX/UI 的痛点往往在 Figma 之外 ：比如真实数","category":"资源&工具","tags":["PART1️⃣ AI设计工作流&Vibe Coding","资源&工具"],"featured":false,"order":31,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2026-03-07","wordCount":1334,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/naidlfq53mc9ahn7","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"ufca33725\" id=\"ufca33725\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0ff09879\" id=\"u0ff09879\">作为 UX/UI 设计师，我们的核心工作是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud0fb732c\" id=\"ud0fb732c\">定义问题、梳理用户旅程（User Journey）、设计交互状态（States）以及确保最终的视觉与研发交付</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u79c79f6f\" id=\"u79c79f6f\">。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u08b0c661\" id=\"u08b0c661\"><span data-lake-id=\"u361fa35a\" id=\"u361fa35a\">Figma 等工具已经把“静态界面”和“基础原型”做到了极致，但 UX/UI 的痛点往往在</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u61edc9d4\" id=\"u61edc9d4\">Figma 之外</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u19da3f22\" id=\"u19da3f22\">：比如真实数据的填充、复杂业务逻辑的验证、枯燥的竞品走查，以及与前端的交付摩擦。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uce6ab107\" id=\"uce6ab107\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2dacab90\" id=\"u2dacab90\">目前阶段，像 OpenClaw 这样具备计算机控制能力和代码执行能力的 Agent，从 UX/UI 设计师的实际工作流来看，它最擅长扮演一个“长了手的高级交互开发助理”。下面我会分享一下我认为它可以帮助到设计师的几个场景，希望对你有帮助</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7f45a4af\" id=\"u7f45a4af\"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"71abb4b1\" id=\"71abb4b1\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucce1cf5d\" id=\"ucce1cf5d\"> 自动化全链路UX竞品走查</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u1d9e0e70\" id=\"u1d9e0e70\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6331d2d8\" id=\"u6331d2d8\">做新功能调研时，我们经常需要把竞品App或网页的整个操作流程录屏、一帧帧截图、再拼到白板里分析，这极其消耗体力。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uda8380ab\" id=\"uda8380ab\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9ea0b7be\" id=\"u9ea0b7be\">落地玩法：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u26d9a7e1\" id=\"u26d9a7e1\"> 设定一个目标任务，比如“在某竞品网站上完成一次退款申请的完整流程”。OpenClaw 可以利用其浏览器控制能力，自动执行每一步点击，并在发生页面跳转或弹窗时自动截图。最后，它能将这些截图连同每一步的操作说明，按顺序输出成一份 Markdown 格式的交互走查报告，直接为你扫清前期的体力活。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u47e65f47\" id=\"u47e65f47\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1772887065032-f97e75a0-9194-434d-9fe8-011065fcf45a.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u4f50a97d-be4f-4d23-93b1-dd3b1f22227%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u0047462f-cbb6-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A539.5%2C%22height%22%3A324%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image%20320.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A274026%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A647%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%2212'%20COMPETITORS%20HAS%20BEEN%20ANALYZED%20LINKEDIN(LINKEDIN.COM)%20ROBOTA%20UA%20(COBOTA.UA)%20TURBOHIRING(TURBOBIRING.CO)%20GLASSDOOR%20(GLASSDOOR.COM)%20DOU(DOU.UA)%20OTTA(OTTA.COM)%20BAZA%20IT%20(BAZAIT.UA)%20WORK%20UA%20(WORK.UA)%20SKYWORKER(SKSOVORKER.AI)%20INDEED%20(INDEED.UA)%20DJINNI(DJINNIUA)%20NOFLUFFJOBS%20(NOFLUFFJOBS.COM)%20FEATURE%20NAME%2FFUNCTION%20POP%20ONBOARDING%20POPULAR%20COMPANY%20VARIFICATION%20POP%20POPULAR%20VACANCY%20VARIFICATION%20POP%20POPULAR%20POPULAR%20POD%20STATISTICS%20POPULAR%20NEW%20VACANCY%20POP%20POP%20NEW%20COMPANY%20POPULAR%20POP%20MY%20VACANCIES%20POPULAR%20POD%20SETTINGS%20POPULAR%20PROMOTE%20VACANCY%20NOT%20VERY%20POPULAR%20POD%20CANDIDATE%20PAGE%20POPULAR%20POP%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A36%2C%22y%22%3A61%2C%22width%22%3A115%2C%22height%22%3A94%2C%22text%22%3A%2212'%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A153%2C%22y%22%3A133%2C%22width%22%3A216%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22COMPETITORS%20HAS%20BEEN%20ANALYZED%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A539%2C%22y%22%3A192%2C%22width%22%3A106%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22LINKEDIN(LINKEDIN.COM)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A284%2C%22y%22%3A193%2C%22width%22%3A104%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22ROBOTA%20UA%20(COBOTA.UA)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A790%2C%22y%22%3A193%2C%22width%22%3A126%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22