%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22NOT%20VERY%20POPULAR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A789%2C%22y%22%3A594%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22POD%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A35%2C%22y%22%3A626%2C%22width%22%3A76%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22CANDIDATE%20PAGE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1006%2C%22y%22%3A626%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22POPULAR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A791%2C%22y%22%3A626%2C%22width%22%3A22%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22POP%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23080808%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u39ef9042%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"4a2e500b\" id=\"4a2e500b\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u22e04610\" id=\"u22e04610\"> 建立私人自动化的情绪板</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ud55d938e\" id=\"ud55d938e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u92b3b5f2\" id=\"u92b3b5f2\">当你在探索特定的视觉风格时——例如想要在一套新的界面中尝试“弥散渐变”、“Aura情感光晕” 或是硬核的“粗野主义”排版，手动收集高质量参考非常低效。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8e3b7086\" id=\"u8e3b7086\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf7237724\" id=\"uf7237724\">落地玩法：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc1307490\" id=\"uc1307490\"> 让 OpenClaw 在后台定期巡视 Awwwards、Godly、Mobbin等平台。只要识别到符合特定视觉特征或标签的设计，就自动抓取高分辨率大图，并按照你的个人习惯（按组件类型、按色彩倾向）重命名并分类到本地文件夹。这就相当于你有了一个 24 小时全天候运转的灵感捕获网。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u132a3d43\" id=\"u132a3d43\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1772887080532-53d8d72a-e7d8-474f-b233-d198a97728f3.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud9773eff-99f3-4914-b447-542095a4182%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u0047462f-cbb6-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A539.5%2C%22height%22%3A324%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image%20321.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A631640%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%