 1 的项目，甚至是打造一人公司的产品矩阵，手动对齐设计资产极其痛苦。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud5fb53cf\" id=\"ud5fb53cf\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u91bc32a5\" id=\"u91bc32a5\">落地玩法：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u77299238\" id=\"u77299238\"> 当你在 Figma 中更新了 Design Tokens（颜色、间距、圆角等变量）并导出 JSON 后，让 OpenClaw 接管后续工作。它可以自动读取这个文件，将其转换为前端项目所需的 CSS 变量、Tailwind 配置文件或跨平台的样式表，甚至直接帮你拉分支、提交 PR 到代码仓库。你只需掌控视觉源头，它负责向代码库分发。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufe30bb2f\" id=\"ufe30bb2f\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1772887096681-1d87ab94-e543-4048-ae6a-53f4049a1213.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub3a647a3-3bb1-47d4-8596-209383939ad%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u0047462f-cbb6-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A539.5%2C%22height%22%3A324%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image%20323.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A308991%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A647%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22LIMITED%20ISOLATION%20ALIAS%20TOKEN%20TOOLTIP%20BUTTON%20COLOR_BACKGROUND_PRIMARY%20LABEL%20MEDIUM%20LMPACT%20UPDATES%20%2300A65D%20GREEN_400%20ALIAS%20TOKEN%2001%20COLOR_BORDER_PRIMARY%20BUTTON%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A665%2C%22y%22%3A23%2C%22width%22%3A164%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22LIMITED%20ISOLATION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A575%2C%22y%22%3A99%2C%22width%22%3A116%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22ALIAS%20TOKEN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A880%2C%22y%22%3A119%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22TOOLTIP%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A901%2C%22y%22%3A220%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22BUTTON%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A497%2C%22y%22%3A222%2C%22width%22%3A270%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22COLOR_BACKGROUND_PRIMARY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A880%2C%22y%22%3A311%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%22LABEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A510%2C%22y%22%3A324%2C%22width%22%3A244%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22MEDIUM%20LMPACT%20UPDATES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A95%2C%22y%22%3A403%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22%2300A65D%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A290%2C%22y%22%3A402%2C%22width%22%3A111%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22GREEN_400%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A574%2C%22y%22%3A464%2C%22width%22%3A115%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22ALIAS%20TOKEN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A918%2C%22y%22%3A485%2C%22width%22%3A25%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%2201%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A524%2C%22y%22%3A586%2C%22width%22%3A220%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22COLOR_BORDER_PRIMARY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A902%2C%22y%22%3A588%2C%22width%22%3A69%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22BUTTON%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9f8fd%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u047c7bf9%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"195ca3b0\" id=\"195ca3b0\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub22ca637\" id=\"ub22ca637\">5. 提前入局“面向 Agent 的设计” </span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u624f26ba\" id=\"u624f26ba\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua92ea185\" id=\"ua92ea185\">这是 UX/UI 设计师独有的前瞻性用法。未来的用户可能不再是人，而是另一个帮你点外卖、订机票的 Agent。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u90e679ab\" id=\"u90e679ab\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u97fcc4a8\" id=\"u97fcc4a8\">落地玩法：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9e27fb59\" id=\"u9e27fb59\"> 把 OpenClaw 当作你的“机器用户”来做可用性测试。让它尝试去理解和操作你设计出的网页原型。通过观察它在哪一步卡住、是否能准确识别出设计所表达的内容，你可以反向评估当前的 UI 架构对 AI 是否友好。这能极大提升你在未来 API-First UI 时代的设计认知。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubf6b525c\" id=\"ubf6b525c\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1772887102450-3e6259b4-5fa5-4a66-b160-1b8bce157487.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u5c71172b-ba31-4a5a-be68-9d35d12b748%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u0047462f-cbb6-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A539.5%2C%22height%22%3A324%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image%20319.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A94263%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A647%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22HI%2CLAM%20WYSA!%20YOUR%20AL%20FRIEND%20START%20A%20CHAT%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A542%2C%22y%22%3A242%2C%22width%22%3A178%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22HI%2CLAM%20WYSA!%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A547%2C%22y%22%3A276%2C%22width%22%3A167%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22YOUR%20AL%20FRIEND%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A571%2C%22y%22%3A366%2C%22width%22%3A148%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22START%20A%20CHAT%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e4f0f7%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u38a0b973%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5e649032\" id=\"u5e649032\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u558d194f\" id=\"u558d194f\">总结来说：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufe3f0b1e\" id=\"ufe3f0b1e\"> 对 UX/UI 设计师而言，OpenClaw 现阶段最大的价值不是“帮你画图”，而是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3c7e90ad\" id=\"u3c7e90ad\">打破了设计软件与真实运行环境之间的那堵墙</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3bb25a0d\" id=\"u3bb25a0d\">。它接管了从“静态设计稿”到“动态验证”中间的脏活累活，让你能以近乎单枪匹马的姿态，跑通原本需要一个产研团队才能完成的闭环。</span></p>"}
